== What is {{project_name_long}}? ==
{{project_name_long}} is software designed to preserve security online. It can be installed on computer hardware. It is an operating system.

To learn more about the design and intended user groups, refer to the [[Main Page#overview|wiki main page, overview]].

== How does {{project_name_long}} work? == 
To protect a user's security on the Internet [https://www.{{project_clearnet}}/#features numerous security mechanisms] are deployed. See also [[Main Page]] and [[About]].

{{Anchor|advantages}}
== What are the Advantages of {{project_name_long}}? ==
{{project_name_long}} realistically addresses common attack vectors.

{{project_name_long}} deploys [https://www.{{project_clearnet}}/#features numerous security mechanisms] to mitigate such attacks.

== How is {{project_name_long}} different from others? ==
{{project_name_long}} [[Main Page#design|protects]] you from [[Malware|viruses]].

{{project_name_long}} is a complete operating system (OS). A [[web browser|web browser]], [[Software#Office_Suite|office suite]], and [[Software|more]] come pre-configured with security in mind. See also [[Comparison with Others|Comparison of {{project_name_long}} and Others]].

== Who Develops {{project_name_long}}? ==
{{project_name_long}} is being developed by an independent development [[contributors]].

